00:08:12.270 --> 00:08:17.949
So, I have a virtual follow spot which illuminates
me but does not interfere with the video image.

00:08:17.949 --> 00:08:26.139
I also have a drawing system, a 2-D particle
system, which can sprites and 2-D box physics.

00:08:26.139 --> 00:08:28.490
