to use for different type of productions.

00:08:35.320 --> 00:08:42.079
It can be used for projecting onto masks,
pieces of scenery, buildings and such.

00:08:42.079 --> 00:08:45.490
It's all created in a tool which is called
Open Frameworks.

00:08:45.490 --> 00:08:52.149
It's a C++ library for people who love to
play with multimedia and new media.

